title: instagram
content: We are inspired by the inter-species speculation of flowers and insects, combining species with one another and exploring the possibilities that AI gives us, guiding us toward unexpected places. We want to create living images that do not represent existing beings, but speculate realities that only exist in those interpretable images which are subjected to abstraction.
